Usage: reportAlwaysOnBuffer [-help] [-verbose] [-all  | -powerDomain <power domain name>]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-all                                 # Reports always on buffers available in
                                     # all power domains in the design
                                     # (bool, optional)
-powerDomain <power domain name>     # Specifies the name of the power domain
                                     # to report always on buffers
                                     # (string, optional)
-verbose                             # print out detail infomation
                                     # (bool, optional)